title: Ellicott City native advances to finals in Jeopardy College Championship
text:
Ellicott City native advances to finals in Jeopardy College Championship Gary Tse Submitted photo 
Centennial High grad Gary Tse competes tonight in the two-day finals in the Jeopardy College Championships. He is a fresman at the Naval Academy. 
Centennial High grad Gary Tse competes tonight in the two-day finals in the Jeopardy College Championships. He is a fresman at the Naval Academy. (Submitted photo) Andrew Michaels Caption Healthier food choices in school 
Lunch at Wilde Lake High School includes healthier food choices for the students. Advocates for healthy food in schools rated Howard County the best in Maryland for offering healthy choices to students and promoting awareness of healthy eating. (Algerina Perna, Baltimore Sun video)
